Package com.genologics.ri.step

Class Summary
Actions  
ActionsLink Identifies the resource that represents the actions applied or to be applied by the step.
ArtifactLink Artifact is a child element of input-output-map and provides a link to an Artifact that was either an input or output of the Step for the input-output-map.
AutomaticNextStepLink Identifies the resource that represents the step that was automatically begun when the "Automatically start Next Step" option is enabled in a step's configuration.
AvailableProgram Identifies a program that is available for a step.
ContainerLink Provides a URI linking to a selected container to be used for placement.
CreationInput Typically, provides a URI linking to the input artifact.
EscalatedArtifact Sample next action or step.
Escalation Escalation details.
EscalationRequest  
EscalationReview  
Input Provides input URI links.
InputOutputMap Input-output-map is a child element of Step and relates one of the Step inputs to one of the outputs that was produced for that input.
InstrumentLink The instrument element provides a URI to the selected instrument for the step.
NextAction Sample next action or step.
ObjectFactory This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the com.genologics.ri.step package.
Output Provides a URI linking to the output artifact and reagent label.
OutputPlacement Provides a URI linking to the output artifact and container placement.
Placements The detailed representation of a step's output artifact container placements
PlacementsLink Identifies the resource that represents the output placements for the step.
PooledInputs Provides pooled input groups.
Pools The detailed representation of a step's pooled inputs.
PoolsLink Identifies the resource that represents the pools added by the step.
ProcessStep The detailed representation of a step.
ProgramStatus The current EPP status for a step (supports automatically triggered programs only).
ProgramStatusLink Identifies the resource that represents the program status for the step.
ReagentLabel Reagent-label is a child element of ExtStepReagentListElement and provides the name of a label or reagent that has been added to the Artifact.
ReagentLotLink Provides a URI linking to the reagent lot details.
ReagentLots The list representation of a step's reagent lots.
ReagentLotsLink Identifies the resource that represents the reagent lots for the step.
Reagents The detailed representation of a step's output artifact reagents.
ReagentsLink Identifies the resource that represents the reagents added by the step.
SharedResultFile The file element describes a shared result file output that will be displayed in the step-setup view.
StepConfiguration Identifies the configuration information for the step run.
StepCreation A request to create a step.
StepDetails  
StepDetailsLink Identifies the resource that represents the details for the step.
StepSetup  
StepSetupLink Identifies the resource that represents the setup for the step.
UserLink Describes a user as required in the context of step escalations.
